Detailed Description

template<class T>
class Util::List< T >

Single linked list (thread unsafe)

The list descriptor is linked to the first and last elements. We can define a list of Linkable cells : 

    List<X> Q_of_X;
Warning:
In deletion, a list must be empty. In insertion, cell must be defined ( not 0).
See also:
StackList, Queue
